{"thi-ap40:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap40:0.2":"Khattiyavagga ","thi-ap40:0.3":"10 Pesalatheriapadana ","thi-ap40:1.1":"“Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap40:1.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap40:1.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap40:1.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap40:2.1":"Savatthiyam pure vare, ","thi-ap40:2.2":"upasakakule aham; ","thi-ap40:2.3":"Pasuta tam jinavaram, ","thi-ap40:2.4":"disva sutva ca desanam. ","thi-ap40:3.1":"Tam viram saranam gantva, ","thi-ap40:3.2":"silani ca samadiyim; ","thi-ap40:3.3":"Kadaci so mahaviro, ","thi-ap40:3.4":"mahajanasamagame. ","thi-ap40:4.1":"Attano abhisambodhim, ","thi-ap40:4.2":"pakasesi narasabho; ","thi-ap40:4.3":"Ananussutadhammesu, ","thi-ap40:4.4":"pubbe dukkhadikesu ca. ","thi-ap40:5.1":"Cakkhu nananca panna ca, ","thi-ap40:5.2":"vijjaloko ca asi me; ","thi-ap40:5.3":"Tam sutva uggahetvana, ","thi-ap40:5.4":"paripucchinca bhikkhavo. ","thi-ap40:6.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap40:6.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap40:6.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap40:6.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap40:7.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap40:7.2":"Jata setthimahakule; ","thi-ap40:7.3":"Upecca buddham saddhammam, ","thi-ap40:7.4":"Sutva saccupasamhitam. ","thi-ap40:8.1":"Pabbajitvacireneva, ","thi-ap40:8.2":"saccatthani vicintayam; ","thi-ap40:8.3":"Khepetva asave sabbe, ","thi-ap40:8.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap40:9.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap40:9.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap40:9.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap40:9.4":"vasi homi mahamune. ","thi-ap40:10.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap40:10.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap40:10.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap40:10.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap40:11.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap40:11.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap40:11.3":"Nanam me vimalam suddham, ","thi-ap40:11.4":"buddhasetthassa vahasa. ","thi-ap40:12.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap40:12.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","thi-ap40:12.3":"Nagiva bandhanam chetva, ","thi-ap40:12.4":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap40:13.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap40:13.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","thi-ap40:13.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thi-ap40:13.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap40:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap40:14.2":"Vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","thi-ap40:14.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","thi-ap40:14.4":"Katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap40:15.1":"Ittham sudam pesala bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap40:16.1":"Pesalatheriyapadanam dasamam. ","thi-ap40:16.2":"Khattiyavaggo catuttho. ","thi-ap40:17.1":"Tassuddanam ","thi-ap40:18.1":"Khattiya brahmani ceva, ","thi-ap40:18.2":"tatha uppaladayika; ","thi-ap40:18.3":"Singalamata sukka ca, ","thi-ap40:18.4":"abhirupa addhakasika. ","thi-ap40:19.1":"Punna ca ambapali ca, ","thi-ap40:19.2":"pesalati ca ta dasa; ","thi-ap40:19.3":"Gathayo dvisatanettha, ","thi-ap40:19.4":"dvicattalisa cuttari. ","thi-ap40:20.1":"Atha vagguddanam ","thi-ap40:21.1":"Sumedha ekuposatha, ","thi-ap40:21.2":"kundalakesi khattiya; ","thi-ap40:21.3":"Sahassam tisata gatha, ","thi-ap40:21.4":"sattatalisa pindita. ","thi-ap40:22.1":"Saha uddanagathahi, ","thi-ap40:22.2":"ganitayo vibhavibhi; ","thi-ap40:22.3":"Sahassam tisatam gatha, ","thi-ap40:22.4":"sattapannasameva cati. ","thi-ap40:23.1":"Therikapadanam samattam. ","thi-ap40:24.1":"Apadanapali samatta. "}